snippet.title: Gravewood High - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
An infinitely replayable stealth horror game with roguelike elements and level destruction. 
Play Alpha 1! - http://bit.ly/2GD315c

**About Gravewood High**

Several students have gone missing at Gravewood High but none of the adults seem to have noticed. The school is a trap and your task is to get out of it. But there’s two problems. One, the building has turned into a deadly labyrinth that constantly shifts and changes. Two, you are being chased by the Teacher - a crazed overlord of this place.

#GravewoodHigh
